data.description: It is your chance to own a beautiful three story townhome in Smithfield. On the 1st level, you will find the garage and a flex room. Living areas featuring granite counters and LVP flooring are located on the 2nd floor. The 3rd floor features the primary bedroom with a walk-in closet and ensuite and two spacious bedrooms.
